係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d583bf3acd37d81366eae4c210ef5d0e2298be2","tid":1540864,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd6097415b62d4955ccb67179c5c91ec1f0f7a2","tid":1540864,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18ac0572b2fc87c33b45777c7827587d0512e8f6","tid":1540864,"uid":225130,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"the fight for democracy continues"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"我剛剛都想講呢句, 繼續落去喎, 中咩伏?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"人地意思係階段性勝利，keep going."},{"pid":"3332150c6425d242e1638cea72f9e87b2b93ef08","tid":1540864,"uid":107138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thu